<h2 id="sec-2">Usage</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-2">
</div><div id="outline-container-sec-2-1" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-2-1">Bash</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-2-1">
</div><div id="outline-container-sec-2-1-1" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="sec-2-1-1">Basic Commands</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-1-1">
</div><ul class="org-ul"><li><a id="sec-2-1-1-1" name="sec-2-1-1-1"></a>Navigate file structure<br  /><ul class="org-ul"><li><a id="sec-2-1-1-1-1" name="sec-2-1-1-1-1"></a>ls  (list files in directory)<br  /><div class="outline-text-6" id="text-2-1-1-1-1">
<div class="org-src-container">

<pre class="src src-shell">ls
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</li>
<li><a id="sec-2-1-1-1-2" name="sec-2-1-1-1-2"></a>cd  (change directory)<br  /></li>
<li><a id="sec-2-1-1-1-3" name="sec-2-1-1-1-3"></a>clear (clear terminal display)<br  /></li>
<li><a id="sec-2-1-1-1-4" name="sec-2-1-1-1-4"></a>find (find stuff)<br  /></li></ul>
</li>
<li><a id="sec-2-1-1-2" name="sec-2-1-1-2"></a>Mutate file structure<br  /><ul class="org-ul"><li><a id="sec-2-1-1-2-1" name="sec-2-1-1-2-1"></a>mv  (move file)<br  /></li>
<li><a id="sec-2-1-1-2-2" name="sec-2-1-1-2-2"></a>cp  (copy)<br  /></li>
<li><a id="sec-2-1-1-2-3" name="sec-2-1-1-2-3"></a>rm  (remove)<br  /></li>
<li><a id="sec-2-1-1-2-4" name="sec-2-1-1-2-4"></a>ln  (link)<br  /></li></ul>
</li>
<li><a id="sec-2-1-1-3" name="sec-2-1-1-3"></a>bash vars<br  /><ul class="org-ul"><li><a id="sec-2-1-1-3-1" name="sec-2-1-1-3-1"></a>export (export a variable to the environment ( used for PATH a lot))<br  /></li>
<li><a id="sec-2-1-1-3-2" name="sec-2-1-1-3-2"></a>alias (create an alias for a bash expression)<br  /></li></ul>
</li>
<li><a id="sec-2-1-1-4" name="sec-2-1-1-4"></a>text utilities<br  /><ul class="org-ul"><li><a id="sec-2-1-1-4-1" name="sec-2-1-1-4-1"></a>grep (regex search through text)<br  /></li>
<li><a id="sec-2-1-1-4-2" name="sec-2-1-1-4-2"></a>wc ( word line char count)<br  /></li></ul>
</li>

<li><a id="sec-2-1-1-5" name="sec-2-1-1-5"></a>Network management<br  /><ul class="org-ul"><li><a id="sec-2-1-1-5-1" name="sec-2-1-1-5-1"></a>ip (networking information, and configuration)<br  /></li></ul>
</li>
<li><a id="sec-2-1-1-6" name="sec-2-1-1-6"></a>permissions management<br  /><ul class="org-ul"><li><a id="sec-2-1-1-6-1" name="sec-2-1-1-6-1"></a>su (switch user (default is root))<br  /></li>
<li><a id="sec-2-1-1-6-2" name="sec-2-1-1-6-2"></a>sudo (execute command with root privileges)<br  /></li>
<li><a id="sec-2-1-1-6-3" name="sec-2-1-1-6-3"></a>adduser ( user profile management (create users, add them to groups, etc)<br  /></li>
<li><a id="sec-2-1-1-6-4" name="sec-2-1-1-6-4"></a>chmod  (modify file ownership)<br  /></li></ul>
</li></ul>
</div>

